<div class="media" id="conteudo-{{conteudo.id}}" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick={{action 'openModal' conteudo}}>
  <picture class="media__picture">
    <img class="media__thumb" id="file-{{conteudo.id}}" src={{thumbnail}} alt="{{conteudo.titulo}}">
  </picture>
  <div class="media__body flow-md">
    <div class="flex flex-col flow-xxs">
      <span class="title-aux">{{conteudo.tema.name}}</span>
      <span class="media__title title-3">{{conteudo.titulo}}</span>
      <p class="media__descricao-biblioteca">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed sit amet vulputate metus. Vestibulum malesuada sem ac hendrerit convallis. Maecenas vitae pulvinar magna. Maecenas vitae lectus facilisis, semper leo sit amet, feugiat odio.</p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>